    "We also examined the possibility of algorithmic bias in the predictions made by GPT-4 and GPT-3.5, as well as the differences in LLM performance on de-identified versions of patient notes.",
    "These methods have the potential to provide greater access to existing SDoH data that is valuable for retrospective research, chart review for prospective trials, and population health interventions to identify those who might benefit from proactive outreach.",
